@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yfcbui(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.07) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.64)) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.87 / v2 + 0.05)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = (v0 * 0.27)
    tmp = (v0 + (0.85 + (tmp + 0.78 * v0 + 0.89)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
